Package: halDRC
Title: HAL-based Plugin Estimation of the Causal Dose-Response Curve
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Junming", "Shi", email = "junming_shi@berkeley.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package implements the plugin estimator for causal dose-response curves using Highly Adaptive Lasso (HAL), as described in Shi et al. (2024). It supports data-adaptive HAL fitting, undersmoothing, and delta-method based inference via influence curve calculations.
